4:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話時話，唔係太識嘢<br />\n點分100m 500m 1000m router？</blockquote><br />\n你要睇兩樣野<br />\n一個係WAN 一個叫LAN 唔係就咁睇個盒寫什麼800Mbps就當佢係個個速度<br />\n因為盒寫住個個多數都係講Wifi 作大個數黎呃鳩唔識睇既人<br />\n我是但搵份做例子 入面有個叫Number of Ethernet Ports<br />\n寫住Five (5) 10/100/1000 Mbps&mdash;(1 WAN &amp; 4 LAN) Gigabit Ethernet ports<br />\n即係呢隻野最高可以玩到1Gbps 或者直接認Gigabit Ethernet都可以<br />\n咁其他都係一樣 睇返LAN/WAN/Ethernet呢d keyword去搵數字出黎睇就OK<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.netgear.com/home/products/networking/wifi-routers/R7000.aspx#tab-techspecs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.netgear.com%2Fhome%2Fproducts%2Fnetworking%2Fwifi-routers%2FR7000.aspx%23tab-techspecs&d=tg2x2Vtgsuxlq6ErvfvNjr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f5babe41\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.netgear.com/home/products/networking/wifi-routers/R7000.aspx#tab-techspecs</a>"},{"pid":"144a7603f144dbc60bec5b1d69d12bdd01e0dd2e","tid":162260,"uid":45301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:19:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭單問下屋企大約500呎，係想全間屋都收到唔會自動轉4g，有咩推介？越平越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n500尺無實心牆亂買一隻都得</blockquote><br />\n但宜家用緊果個有時係廳同廁所都收唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似係TP LINK，呢個牌子係咪大伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410e66a311cfaf67c2370d74d57958403453d339","tid":162260,"uid":45301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:20:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搭單問下屋企大約500呎，係想全間屋都收到唔會自動轉4g，有咩推介？越平越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n500尺無實心牆亂買一隻都得</blockquote><br />\n但宜家用緊果個有時係廳同廁所都收唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似係TP LINK，呢個牌子係咪大伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋我個router